The Experimental College(EC)s M.A./Dance/Yoga Room provides Martial Arts, dance, and Yoga teaching space for a multitude of classes. Is is located on the second floor of the South Silo Building, Rm.280, above the Silo Bookstore (Law).

It has ballet bars, mirrors on two opposing walls, and a bunch of cubbies. When used for Martial Arts classes the hardwood floor is covered with mats.  Yoga mats are available for Yoga classes.  It also has a great sound system.

The  M.A./Dance/Yoga Room is usually locked, but the space may be used for practice if prearanged with the Experimental College EC Manager (530.752.2568).
